lue":"<p>Ein Rucksack hat 30 Liter Fassungsvermögen oder kann 30 Pfund / 14 Kg Ausrüstung aufnehmen. Du kannst auch Gegenstände außen an dem Rucksack festzurren, wie etwa einen Schlafsack oder ein Seil.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"SHB S. 153","quantity":1,"weight":5,"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"","identified":true,"capacity":{"type":"weight","value":30,"weightless":false},"currency":{"cp":0,"sp":0,"ep":0,"gp":0,"pp":0}},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Adventuring Gear","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":true,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Container"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}]},"id":1180900819,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":105193363,"containerEntityTypeId":1581111423,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":20,"originalName":"Backpack","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/containers/bags/pack-rounded-leather-brown.webp","_id":"rrg6ZtLX1cqm5nMI","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155180,"modifiedTime":1693094071319,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Laute","type":"tool","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Eine Laute, die Ehrfurcht, Verwunderung oder Furcht in Ihrem Publikum hervorruft.</p>\n<p>Bist du im Umgang mit einem Musikinstrument geübt, darfst du deinen Übungsbonus auf alle Attributs- und Fertigkeitswürfe addieren, die mit dem Spielen des Instruments in Verbindung stehen. Ein Barde kann sein Instrument als Zauberfokus, anstelle einer Materialkomponente, für die keine Kosten aufgeführt sind, verwenden. Jedes Musikinstrument benötigt seine eigene Übung.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"SHB S. 154","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":{"value":35,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"toolType":"music","baseItem":"lute","ability":"dex","chatFlavor":"","proficient":1,"bonus":""},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Tool","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":false,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Instrument"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}],"stackable":true},"id":1180900827,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":105193363,"containerEntityTypeId":1581111423,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":131,"originalName":"Lute","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/tools/instruments/lute-gold-brown.webp","_id":"hgOsJxIw7hNvzgnU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155181,"modifiedTime":1693094044152,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Schlafsack","type":"loot","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Stoffrolle, von Reisenden zum Schlafen verwendet.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"SHB S. 150","quantity":1,"weight":7,"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Adventuring Gear","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":false,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Utility"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}],"stackable":true},"id":1180900821,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":1180900819,"containerEntityTypeId":1439493548,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":24,"originalName":"Bedroll","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/sundries/survival/bedroll-pink.webp","_id":"eWSfI1mhtvKrtqN1","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155181,"modifiedTime":1693094044152,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Kerze","type":"consumable","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Eine Kerze spendet für eine Stundes helles Licht in einem Radius von 1,50 m und dämmriges Licht in weiteren 1,50 m Entfernung.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"SHB S. 152","quantity":5,"weight":0,"price":{"value":0.01,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"cover":null,"crewed":false,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","recovery":"","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":null,"attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Adventuring Gear","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":false,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Utility","Exploration","Consumable"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}],"stackable":true},"id":1180900823,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":1180900819,"containerEntityTypeId":1439493548,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":31,"originalName":"Candle","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/sundries/lights/candle-unlit-white.webp","_id":"Snz8bloqjxgeI4bg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155181,"modifiedTime":1693094044153,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Clothes, Costume","type":"loot","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This set of clothes is fashioned after a particular costume, typically meant for entertaining.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"Basic Rules, Player's Handbook","quantity":2,"weight":4,"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Adventuring Gear","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":false,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Social","Deception","Outerwear"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}],"stackable":true},"id":1180900822,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":1180900819,"containerEntityTypeId":1439493548,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":39,"originalName":"Clothes, Costume","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-carved-wood-pink.webp","_id":"ZNFKOF3f7woyDvgA","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155182,"modifiedTime":1692382155182,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Trinkschlauch","type":"backpack","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Eine Lederhaut, die zu einer geschlossenen Form vernäht ist und bis zu 2 Liter Flüssigkeit enthalten kann. Gefüllt wiegt sie 5 Pfund; ein Liter Wasser wiegt etwa 2 Pfund.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"SHB S. 150","quantity":1,"weight":5,"price":{"value":0.2,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"capacity":{"type":"weight","value":0,"weightless":false},"currency":{"cp":0,"sp":0,"ep":0,"gp":0,"pp":0}},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Adventuring Gear","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":false,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Container"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}],"stackable":true},"id":1180900825,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":1180900819,"containerEntityTypeId":1439493548,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":92,"originalName":"Waterskin","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/sundries/survival/wetskin-leather-purple.webp","_id":"ODsFfqM8aawPPCVR","folder":null,"sort":50000,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155183,"modifiedTime":1693094543539,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Verkleidungsausrüstung","type":"tool","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Dieser Beutel mit Schminke, Haarfärbemitteln und kleinen Requisiten lässt dich Verkleidungen entwerfen, die dein Äußeres verändern.</p>\n<p>Bist du im Umgang mit diesem Werkzeug geübt, darfst du deinen Übungsbonus auf alle Attributs- und Fertigkeitswürfe addieren, wenn du dich äußerlich verkleidest.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"Gear"},"source":"SHB S. 154","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"toolType":"","baseItem":"disg","ability":"int","chatFlavor":"","proficient":1,"bonus":""},"flags":{"ddbimporter":{"dndbeyond":{"type":"Tool","isConsumable":false,"isContainer":false,"isCustomItem":false,"isHomebrew":false,"isMonkWeapon":false,"isPack":false,"levelInfusionGranted":null,"tags":["Utility","Deception"],"sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":1}],"stackable":true},"id":1180900826,"entityTypeId":1439493548,"containerEntityId":1180900819,"containerEntityTypeId":1439493548,"definitionEntityTypeId":2103445194,"definitionId":119,"originalName":"Disguise Kit","version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"infusions":{"maps":[],"applied":[],"infused":false}},"effects":[],"img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-carved-scream-tan.webp","_id":"CdwcyAaq56lL9my1","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155183,"modifiedTime":1693094044153,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Magische Dunkelheit breitet sich von einem Punkt deiner Wahl in Reichweite aus (auch um Ecken und füllt für die Wirkungsdauer eine Sphäre mit einem Radius von 4,50 m. Selbst Kreaturen mit Dunkelsicht vermögen den Bereich mit Blicken nicht zu durchdringen und nicht-magisches Licht kann ihn nicht erhellen.</p><p>Ist der gewählte Punkt ein Gegenstand, breitet sich die Dunkelheit von dem Gegenstand aus und bewegt sich mit ihm, falls eine Kreatur ihn trägt oder in der Hand hält. Wird die Quelle der Dunkelheit vollständig mit einem blickdichten Gegenstand bedeckt, wie einer Schüssel oder einem Helm, blockiert das die Dunkelheit.</p><p>Überschneidet sich die Sphäre mit einem Bereich magischen Lichts, der mit einem Spruch des 2. oder eines niedrigeren Grades erschaffen wurde, wird der Zauber aufgehoben, der das Licht verursacht.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SHB S. 223","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"10","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"crewed":false,"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":18,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"evo","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"Fledermausfell und ein Tropfen Pech oder ein Stück Kohle","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"innate","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"name":"Dunkelheit","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"id":205,"definitionId":2058,"entityTypeId":420821570,"dndbeyond":{"lookup":"race","lookupName":"Infernal Legacy","lookupId":62,"race":"Tiefling","level":null,"ability":"cha","mod":4,"dc":15,"overrideDC":false,"id":205,"entityTypeId":420821570,"healingBoost":0,"usesSpellSlot":false},"originalName":"Darkness","sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":230,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Control"],"version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"midiProperties":{"magicdam":true,"magiceffect":true}},"img":"icons/magic/unholy/orb-glowing-purple.webp","effects":[],"_id":"9GGf1tlQDOnGv45T","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155183,"modifiedTime":1695499809189,"lastModifiedBy":"sjYkV3qNoQe97JYZ"}},{"type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Du deutest mit einem Finger und die Kreatur, die dich verletzt hat, wird für einen kurzen Moment von höllischen Flammen eingehüllt. Die Kreatur muss einen Geschicklichkeitsrettungswurf ablegen. Bei einem Misserfolg erleidet das Ziel 2W10 Feuerschaden oder halb so viel Schaden bei einem erfolgreichen Rettungswurf.</p>\n<p><strong>Auf höheren Graden: </strong>Wenn du diesen Spruch mit einem Zauberplatz des 2. oder eines höheren Grades wirkst, steigt der Schaden für jeden Grad über den 1. hinaus um 1W10.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SHB S. 240","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"which you take in response to being damaged by a creature within 60 feet of you that you can see"},"duration":{"value":"","units":"inst"},"cover":null,"crewed":false,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":18,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d10[fire]","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"innate","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d10"}},"name":"Höllischer Tadel","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"id":204,"definitionId":2142,"entityTypeId":420821570,"dndbeyond":{"lookup":"race","lookupName":"Infernal Legacy","lookupId":62,"race":"Tiefling","level":2,"ability":"cha","mod":4,"dc":15,"overrideDC":false,"id":204,"entityTypeId":420821570,"healingBoost":0,"usesSpellSlot":false},"originalName":"Hellish Rebuke","sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":250,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Damage"],"version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"midiProperties":{"magicdam":true,"magiceffect":true}},"img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-shadow-monster-red.webp","effects":[],"_id":"tuwwOomx2MqjpONQ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155184,"modifiedTime":1695501750240,"lastModifiedBy":"sjYkV3qNoQe97JYZ"}},{"type":"spell","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Du manifestierst ein kleines Wunder in Reichweite, ein Zeichen übernatürlicher Macht. Du kannst einen der folgenden magischen Effekte erzeugen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Deine Stimme dröhnt für 1 Minute dreimal so laut wie normal.</li>\n<li>Du lässt Flammen flackern, heller oder dunkler werden oder die Farbe wechseln. Der Effekt hält 1 Minute an.</li>\n<li>Du erzeugst für 1 Minute harmlose Erschütterungen des Bodens.</li>\n<li>Du erschaffst ein kurzes Geräusch, das von einem Punkt deiner Wahl in Reichweite ertönt, wie das Grollen von Donner, den Ruf eines Raben oder ein unheilvolles Flüstern.</li>\n<li>Du lässt eine nicht verriegelte Tür oder ein Fenster auffliegen oder zuschlagen.</li>\n<li>Du änderst für 1 Minute das Aussehen deiner Augen.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Wenn du diesen Zauber mehrmals wirkst, können bis zu drei der nicht sofortigen Effekte gleichzeitig aktiv sein. Du kannst solche Effekte als Aktion aufheben.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SHB S. 272","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"minute"},"cover":null,"crewed":false,"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":9,"long":null,"units":"m"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"trs","components":{"vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"name":"Thaumaturgie","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"id":203,"definitionId":2277,"entityTypeId":420821570,"dndbeyond":{"lookup":"race","lookupName":"Infernal Legacy","lookupId":62,"race":"Tiefling","level":null,"ability":"cha","mod":4,"dc":15,"overrideDC":false,"id":203,"entityTypeId":420821570,"healingBoost":0,"usesSpellSlot":false},"originalName":"Thaumaturgy","sources":[{"sourceId":1,"pageNumber":null,"sourceType":2},{"sourceId":2,"pageNumber":282,"sourceType":1}],"tags":["Control"],"version":"3.4.57","importId":"H5jtN7tByd3SNWB0"},"midiProperties":{"magicdam":true,"magiceffect":true}},"img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-teal.webp","effects":[],"_id":"Cd9CJiE2pfjRr0kD","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1692382155184,"modifiedTime":1693094044154,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"}},{"name":"Nimmervoller Beutel","type":"backpack","img":"icons/containers/bags/pouch-leather-pink.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Wundersamer Gegenstand, ungewöhnlich</em></p>\n<p>Dieser Beutel hat einen Innenraum, der erheblich größer ist als seine Außenabmessungen, ungefähr 0,6 Meter Durchmesser an der Öffnung und 1,2 Meter Tiefe. Der Beutel kann bis zu 500 Pfund tragen,jedoch nicht mehr als ein Volumen von 1,75 Kubikmeter. Der Beutel wiegt unabhängig von seinem Inhalt 15 Pfund. Ein Objekt aus dem Beutel zu holen, erfordert eine Aktion. Wenn der Beutel überlastet, durchbohrt oder zerrissen wird, platzt er und wird zerstört, und sein Inhalt ist in der Astralebene zerstreut. Wenn der Beutel nach innen gedreht wird, wird sein Inhalt unversehrt verschüttet, aber der Beutel muss richtig herumgedreht werden, bevor er erneut verwendet werden kann.</p>\n<p>Atmende Wesen im Inneren des Beutels können bis zu 10 Minuten darin überleben, wobei die Minuten geteilt werden durch die Anzahl der darin befindlichen Kreaturen (mindestens 1 Minute pro Kopf). Nach dieser Zeit beginnen sie zu ersticken.</p>\n<p>Das Platzieren eines <em>Nimmervollen Beutels</em> in einem extradimensionalen Raum, der beispielsweise von <em>Hewards Praktischem Rucksack</em>, einem <em>Tragbaren Loch</em> oder einem ähnlichen Gegenstand geschaffen wurde, zerstört beide Gegenstände sofort und öffnet ein Tor zur Astralebene. Das Tor entsteht dort, wo der eine Gegenstand innerhalb des anderen platziert wurde.Jede Kreatur innerhalb von 3 m des Tores wird hindurch gesogen zu einem willkürlichen Ort auf der Astralebene. Das Tor schließt sich daraufhin. Das Tor ist einseitig und kann nicht wieder geöffnet werden.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SLH S. 173","quantity":1,"weight":15,"price":{"value":4000,"denomination":"gp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"capacity":{"type":"weight","value":500,"weightless":true},"currency":{"cp":0,"sp":0,"ep":0,"gp":0,"pp":0}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":100000,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Bag of Holding"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.items.aDHRuUs29SrumWfq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1661787233722,"modifiedTime":1693094563182,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"_id":"vFHZX0Tq2HGPMc8S"},{"_id":"tvNhzIiOD4Qcwoo9","name":"Seife","type":"loot","img":"icons/sundries/survival/soap.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Wird zum Reinigen und Waschen verwendet.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SHB S. 150","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"cp"},"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"has